WEBVTT

00:05.098 --> 00:06.567
[ Buzzing ]

00:06.600 --> 00:07.901
There. All done.

00:07.934 --> 00:09.302
Let me show you
the back.

00:09.335 --> 00:10.503
Perfect.

00:10.537 --> 00:11.504
Perfect.

00:11.538 --> 00:12.673
Perfect.

00:12.706 --> 00:13.674
Perfect.

00:13.707 --> 00:14.875
Perfect.

00:14.908 --> 00:15.876
Perfect.

00:15.909 --> 00:16.943
Perfect.

00:16.977 --> 00:17.944
Perfect.

00:17.978 --> 00:18.945
Perfect.

00:18.979 --> 00:20.046
[ Gasps ]

00:20.080 --> 00:21.014
Perfect.

00:21.047 --> 00:22.082
Same time tomorrow?

00:22.115 --> 00:23.283
Of course, sir.

00:23.316 --> 00:24.484
[ Vacuum whirring ]

00:24.517 --> 00:25.586
[ Bells jingle ]

00:27.187 --> 00:29.590
Oh, Mr. Watterson.
I didn't see you there.

00:29.623 --> 00:30.924
So, how can I help?

00:30.957 --> 00:31.992
Just a trim, please.

00:32.025 --> 00:33.594
Something like this.

00:33.627 --> 00:35.796
Uh, sir, there is
a slight problem.

00:35.829 --> 00:37.764
If you're worried I can't pay,
I can assure you

00:37.798 --> 00:39.633
I went through my wife's purse
this morning.

00:39.666 --> 00:41.868
Actually, I had
another concern.

00:41.902 --> 00:44.337
You, uh,
appear to be...

00:44.370 --> 00:45.305
bald.

00:45.338 --> 00:47.608
[ "Bald" echoing ]

00:50.811 --> 00:52.979
[ High-pitched scream ]

00:53.013 --> 00:54.280
I'm not bald!

00:54.314 --> 00:55.415
Bald people are a joke!

00:55.448 --> 00:56.717
Uh, I'm bald, sir.

00:56.750 --> 00:57.718
Exactly!

00:57.751 --> 00:59.352
Listen,
I came here for a haircut!

00:59.385 --> 01:02.388
I'm not leaving
until I get one!

01:02.422 --> 01:03.857
Hmm.

01:03.890 --> 01:05.759
[ Wind blows ]

01:05.792 --> 01:07.527
Uh, are you sure?

01:07.560 --> 01:08.695
Yes!

01:08.729 --> 01:10.797
[ Dramatic music plays ]

01:12.265 --> 01:13.867
[ Operatic crescendo ]

01:13.900 --> 01:15.836
[ Creaking ]

01:22.976 --> 01:24.778
Is everything okay?

01:24.811 --> 01:26.713
Mm-hmm.

01:26.747 --> 01:27.881
Disgraceful!

01:27.914 --> 01:29.549
First, he gives me
this insult of a haircut,

01:29.582 --> 01:31.517
then he has the audacity
to call me bald!

01:31.551 --> 01:33.687
Me -- Richard Watterson!
How dare he...

01:33.720 --> 01:35.155
How long's he been going on
like this?

01:35.188 --> 01:36.156
What?!

01:36.189 --> 01:37.658
[ Sighs ]

01:37.691 --> 01:40.260
Dude, you don't have ears.
Where did you put those?

01:40.293 --> 01:41.762
Oh. So that's why
they didn't work.

01:41.795 --> 01:43.864
So, how long has he been
going on like this?

01:43.897 --> 01:45.398
About three days.

01:45.431 --> 01:47.467
Mr. Dad, why didn't you just
tell Larry there and then

01:47.500 --> 01:48.935
that you weren't happy?

01:48.969 --> 01:50.804
And waste my precious breath
on someone so deluded?!

01:50.837 --> 01:53.674
I mean, do I look like a guy
who's lost his hair?!

01:53.707 --> 01:54.675
Uh, stand still.

01:54.708 --> 01:55.776
It's kind of hard to tell

01:55.809 --> 01:57.343
with the light
bouncing off your head.

01:57.377 --> 01:58.144
Hmph!

01:58.178 --> 01:59.680
Dad,
you've got to step up

01:59.713 --> 02:00.747
and do the right thing.

02:00.781 --> 02:02.348
Leave a mean review about Larry
online

02:02.382 --> 02:04.184
and ruin his life
with complete anonymity.

02:04.217 --> 02:07.754
Hmm. That's both lazy
and cowardly.

02:07.788 --> 02:09.189
Pass me the laptop.

02:09.222 --> 02:11.457
[ Classical guitar music plays ]

02:22.035 --> 02:23.136
[ Computer chiming ]

02:23.169 --> 02:25.238
Agh!
Anyone know my login?

02:25.271 --> 02:26.472
I've forgotten it.
[ Sighs ]

02:26.506 --> 02:27.874
Okay, what do you want
to say?

02:27.908 --> 02:30.777
"I left this hairdresser
a sad, broken man."

02:30.811 --> 02:32.713
Dad, you went in
a sad, broken man.

02:32.746 --> 02:34.347
The key to a good online review
is to take out

02:34.380 --> 02:35.882
all the frustration you have
in your life

02:35.916 --> 02:38.318
on someone who totally
doesn't deserve it.

02:38.351 --> 02:39.485
[ Classical guitar music plays ]

02:39.519 --> 02:41.121
[ Winces ] Ooh!
[ Winces ] Ooh!

02:41.154 --> 02:42.122
Mm... Mm...

02:42.155 --> 02:43.189
Oh! Oh!

02:43.223 --> 02:44.758
And viola.

02:44.791 --> 02:46.760
And...send!

02:46.793 --> 02:48.228
[ Telephone rings ]

02:48.261 --> 02:49.429
Hello?
It's Larry.

02:49.462 --> 02:50.764
[ Gasps ]
It's Larry.

02:50.797 --> 02:52.432
It's Larry!
[ Gasps ]
It's Larry!

02:52.465 --> 02:53.666
[ Gasps ]
It's Larry?

02:53.700 --> 02:55.301
Uh, yes, it's Larry.

02:55.335 --> 02:56.737
I'm calling
about your review.

02:56.770 --> 02:58.739
How are you so sure
it was me?

02:58.772 --> 02:59.873
I used a fake name.

02:59.906 --> 03:02.642
Well, actually, you signed
the review "Richard."

03:02.675 --> 03:04.644
But I meant
a different Richard.

03:04.677 --> 03:06.479
A different
Richard Watterson?

03:06.512 --> 03:08.214
I have a very common name.

03:08.248 --> 03:09.515
You uploaded your photo.

03:09.549 --> 03:11.417
I...have
a very common face?

03:11.451 --> 03:13.754
What you said was
uncalled for, mean,

03:13.787 --> 03:15.455
and, frankly,
full of grammatical errors.

03:15.488 --> 03:18.591
But it's my philosophy that
the customer is always right,

03:18.624 --> 03:20.393
so if you take down
the review,

03:20.426 --> 03:22.796
you can get free haircuts
for you and your family.

03:22.829 --> 03:24.597
And...?
[ Sighs ]

03:24.630 --> 03:26.867
And you have
a thick head of hair.

03:26.900 --> 03:27.868
How thick?

03:27.901 --> 03:28.869
Quite thick?

03:28.902 --> 03:30.070
I'll take it!

03:30.103 --> 03:31.437
Now, if you kids
will excuse me,

03:31.471 --> 03:33.807
I'm off to buy a com-b.

03:33.840 --> 03:35.475
Did you see
what happened there?

03:35.508 --> 03:37.077
All we have to do is threaten
Larry with a bad review,

03:37.110 --> 03:38.278
and he'll give us
free stuff!

03:38.311 --> 03:39.445
And that guy works
everywhere!

03:39.479 --> 03:40.914
It's a victimless crime!

03:40.947 --> 03:42.182
Apart from Larry.

03:42.215 --> 03:43.750
Effortless.
It's an effortless crime.

03:43.784 --> 03:45.752
Gumball: [ Strained ]
Dude, we ate too much.

03:45.786 --> 03:47.220
I'm gonna
loosen my belt.

03:47.253 --> 03:49.355
[ Strained ] Me too.

03:49.389 --> 03:50.356
[ Both belch ]

03:50.390 --> 03:51.758
Both: Belly five!

03:51.792 --> 03:53.760
I hope everything
was to your liking, gentlemen.

03:53.794 --> 03:54.795
Here's your check.

03:54.828 --> 03:56.562
Uh, I don't think
we'll be paying.

03:56.596 --> 03:58.598
And why would I give you
a free meal?

03:58.631 --> 04:00.000
Because that's
the sort of generous touch

04:00.033 --> 04:02.836
that guarantees you
a glowing five-star review!

04:02.869 --> 04:04.037
I don't think so.

04:04.070 --> 04:05.338
Four stars it is, then.

04:05.371 --> 04:06.807
[ Gasps ]
Hey, stop that!

04:06.840 --> 04:08.875
One bad review online is
all it takes

04:08.909 --> 04:10.276
to drag a place down!

04:10.310 --> 04:12.078
Talking back to a customer?
Three stars.

04:12.112 --> 04:13.313
[ Patrons screaming ]

04:13.346 --> 04:14.514
Take it down to two.

04:14.547 --> 04:16.182
Maybe we can get
a free dessert.

04:16.216 --> 04:17.383
[ Gasps ]

04:17.417 --> 04:20.553
Want to try
for one star, Larry?

04:20.586 --> 04:22.755
[ Screams ] Okay, okay,
your meal is free!

04:22.789 --> 04:24.457
Five stars.
Would come again.

04:24.490 --> 04:25.992
We'll take the desserts
to go.

04:26.026 --> 04:26.993
We don't do takeout --

04:27.027 --> 04:27.994
Hmm?

04:28.028 --> 04:29.162
[ Sighs ]

04:29.195 --> 04:31.097
Gumball:
Boring! Ugh!

04:31.131 --> 04:32.565
Rhinos, flamingos?

04:32.598 --> 04:34.868
I've seen it all before.
There's nothing new here.

04:34.901 --> 04:36.269
It's getting one star.

04:36.302 --> 04:38.038
What?!
You want new animals?!

04:38.071 --> 04:41.007
Breaking the laws of nature
seems kind of wrong.
Hmm?

04:41.041 --> 04:43.576
[ Stammers ] But the customer
is always right!

04:43.609 --> 04:45.245
[ Guttural roaring ]

04:45.278 --> 04:46.913
Ugh! Ugh!

04:46.947 --> 04:48.081
Ta-da!

04:48.114 --> 04:50.716
That...is..horrific.

04:55.421 --> 04:57.623
[ Shakily ]
Five stars.

04:57.657 --> 04:59.860
Lois: So, Man Man,
what can I do for you?

04:59.893 --> 05:01.694
Man Man: Well, Miss Plane,
I was in the area,

05:01.727 --> 05:04.264
and I thought I'd, uh, take
a look at your tax returns.

05:04.297 --> 05:05.565
This movie is garbage.

05:05.598 --> 05:06.867
What superhero is this?

05:06.900 --> 05:07.868
Man Man!

05:07.901 --> 05:08.801
He was bitten by a man

05:08.835 --> 05:10.270
and given the powers
of a man.

05:10.303 --> 05:11.604
Yeah, that's weak.

05:11.637 --> 05:12.873
I guess we'll give
the cinema one star.

05:12.906 --> 05:14.674
Wait! We didn't make
the film!

05:14.707 --> 05:15.876
Yeah,
but you showed it.

05:15.909 --> 05:17.443
You should apply
a little quality control

05:17.477 --> 05:18.778
before stealing
two hours of our lives.

05:18.811 --> 05:20.680
Plus ads.
Four hours of our lives.

05:20.713 --> 05:22.883
[ Sighs ] All right.
Give me a minute.

05:22.916 --> 05:24.384
Man Man:
But give it back --

05:24.417 --> 05:25.886
[ Audio slows, stops ]

05:25.919 --> 05:27.553
Larry:
Great game today.

05:27.587 --> 05:30.423
Yeah, we're going all the way
to the state finals.

05:30.456 --> 05:31.457
[ Gasps ]

05:31.491 --> 05:32.959
Who's that?

05:32.993 --> 05:34.127
That?! Ha!

05:34.160 --> 05:35.595
She's just some nerdy girl

05:35.628 --> 05:37.998
that will never get
with hot jocks like us.

05:38.031 --> 05:40.200
[ Laughs ]

05:40.233 --> 05:41.201
Troy?

05:41.234 --> 05:43.469
[ Soft guitar music plays ]

05:45.438 --> 05:48.041
You know,
without these glasses,

05:48.074 --> 05:49.509
you're beautiful.

05:49.542 --> 05:51.711
When did you know you were
going to ask me to the prom?

05:51.744 --> 05:53.980
From the moment
our eyes met.

05:54.014 --> 05:55.681
♪ I remember last year

05:55.715 --> 05:59.552
♪ I wanted to see your face

06:01.487 --> 06:02.989
What was that?

06:03.023 --> 06:03.990
Darwin: [ Sobbing ]

06:04.024 --> 06:06.459
I never thought
they'd get together.

06:06.492 --> 06:08.228
They were so different.

06:08.261 --> 06:09.795
They were literally
the same guy.

06:09.829 --> 06:11.998
[ Sniffles ]
Five stars!

06:12.032 --> 06:12.999
Hey!

06:13.033 --> 06:14.000
Ugh!
One star!

06:14.034 --> 06:15.868
Dude, you can't review
Tobias.

06:15.902 --> 06:17.737
He's not a business.

06:17.770 --> 06:18.905
Hmm.

06:18.939 --> 06:21.074
Larry, we need you
to design us a website.

06:21.107 --> 06:22.508
But this is a shoe store.

06:22.542 --> 06:24.677
A shoe store with
a very poor web-design service.

06:24.710 --> 06:26.446
Larry,
raise my eyebrow for me.

06:26.479 --> 06:27.747
[ Sighs ]

06:29.149 --> 06:31.117
[ Screams ]
Right away!

06:31.151 --> 06:32.885
[ Keyboard clacking, beep ]

06:32.919 --> 06:33.886
It's online.

06:33.920 --> 06:34.988
Perfect!

06:36.222 --> 06:37.357
[ Cellphone chimes ]

06:37.390 --> 06:38.524
I got reviewed?

06:38.558 --> 06:40.193
One star?!

06:40.226 --> 06:41.594
[ Groans ]

06:42.328 --> 06:43.763
Too small and round.
One star.

06:43.796 --> 06:44.797
Hey!

06:44.830 --> 06:46.632
Has the dress sense
of a fever dream

06:46.666 --> 06:47.867
and is easily confused.

06:47.900 --> 06:50.236
Hey!
I dyed this tie myself!

06:50.270 --> 06:51.637
Or is it "tied this dye"?

06:51.671 --> 06:52.605
Ugh!

06:52.638 --> 06:54.274
The sun's too hot!
One star?

06:54.307 --> 06:57.043
Would not recommend
to a nearby solar system.

06:57.077 --> 06:58.278
Rate me one star?

06:58.311 --> 06:59.879
I am one star!

06:59.912 --> 07:01.814
Principal Brown.
What happened?

07:01.847 --> 07:03.816
I got a terrible review
online.

07:03.849 --> 07:05.785
One star?
No, it was three stars,

07:05.818 --> 07:07.387
but the student made
so many spelling errors,

07:07.420 --> 07:09.155
the school board
sacked me anyway.

07:09.189 --> 07:10.190
Want to buy a pirate DVD?

07:10.223 --> 07:11.457
Absolutely not.

07:11.491 --> 07:12.558
[ Groans ]

07:12.592 --> 07:13.726
This is bad, Gumball.

07:13.759 --> 07:15.361
Other people are using
our website

07:15.395 --> 07:16.662
to review everything.

07:16.696 --> 07:18.064
Meh,
what could go wrong?

07:18.098 --> 07:19.465
[ Cellphone chimes ]

07:19.499 --> 07:21.701
I guess the reviewer
has become the reviewee.

07:21.734 --> 07:23.236
Terrible line.
Two stars.
Ohh!

07:23.269 --> 07:24.670
[ Siren wails ]
Felicity:
What's wrong with you?!

07:24.704 --> 07:25.871
Why won't you help me?!

07:25.905 --> 07:27.540
I'm sorry,
but we can't risk it.

07:27.573 --> 07:29.109
Our last review was all,

07:29.142 --> 07:31.511
"Emergency response times this,
medical ethics that."

07:31.544 --> 07:33.246
So I'm supposed to
just lie here?!

07:33.279 --> 07:34.747
Hmm.
Patient very pushy.

07:34.780 --> 07:36.316
One star.
[ Screams ]

07:36.349 --> 07:38.584
Boring accident scene.
One star.
Dude!

07:38.618 --> 07:40.753
Come on! Do something
about these termites!

07:40.786 --> 07:42.155
They're eating my house!

07:42.188 --> 07:44.190
Sorry. I can't afford
any more bad reviews.

07:44.224 --> 07:46.226
Turns out termites have
a strong online presence.

07:46.259 --> 07:47.760
[ Engine starts, tires squeal ]

07:47.793 --> 07:48.961
Agh!

07:48.995 --> 07:50.496
Huh?!

07:50.530 --> 07:53.099
Well, at least
we can sleep in the car.

07:53.133 --> 07:55.101
Huh?!

07:55.135 --> 07:58.838
Well, at least I've still got
my loving wife.

08:00.106 --> 08:01.074
Huh?

08:01.107 --> 08:02.108
Oh, come on!

08:02.142 --> 08:03.776
[ Pigeons cooing ]

08:03.809 --> 08:06.346
Uh...what's going on?

08:06.379 --> 08:07.347
Dad: [ Whimpers ]

08:07.380 --> 08:09.015
Dad?!
What's happening?

08:09.049 --> 08:11.417
The people in the store said
bald guys don't need combs,

08:11.451 --> 08:13.886
so I gave them one star,
so they gave me one star.

08:13.919 --> 08:15.521
What if I lose
that star, too?

08:15.555 --> 08:17.790
What will people I don't know
on the Internet think about me?!

08:17.823 --> 08:20.360
Dad, other people's opinions
don't matter.

08:20.393 --> 08:21.494
Only our opinions matter.

08:21.527 --> 08:22.595
That's why we made
the website!

08:22.628 --> 08:24.197
Terrible logic.
One star!

08:24.230 --> 08:26.066
Aah!
He's got a point,
Gumball.

08:26.099 --> 08:28.434
Not supporting your brother.
One star.
[ Screams ]

08:28.468 --> 08:29.435
Just do nothing.

08:29.469 --> 08:30.503
If you don't do anything,

08:30.536 --> 08:31.637
you can't do
anything wrong,

08:31.671 --> 08:32.872
and you can't get
a bad review.

08:32.905 --> 08:34.474
Well, I guess
if nobody's moving,

08:34.507 --> 08:36.242
nothing bad can happen,
right?

08:36.276 --> 08:39.512
[ Tires squeal, engine revs ]
Terrible driver --
too fast!

08:39.545 --> 08:41.314
Far too slow.

08:41.347 --> 08:42.382
Too jerky!

08:42.415 --> 08:43.949
Grating voice.
One star.

08:43.983 --> 08:45.885
Typing while driving.
One star.

08:45.918 --> 08:47.820
[ Screams ]
Officer! Do something!

08:47.853 --> 08:49.122
[ Snorts ]
Nuh-unh!

08:49.155 --> 08:50.556
I'm on two stars here.

08:50.590 --> 08:52.825
One bad review, and I could be
busted down to traffic cop.

08:52.858 --> 08:54.527
And then
I'd have to do something.

08:54.560 --> 08:56.996
I've got it! We made the website
to give everything bad reviews,

08:57.029 --> 08:58.631
but now
that's stopped everyone.

08:58.664 --> 09:00.233
Maybe if we give the website
a bad review,

09:00.266 --> 09:01.534
that will stop the website.

09:01.567 --> 09:03.436
Clunky overwordy exposition.
Zero star--

09:03.469 --> 09:05.037
Rude interruption!
One star!

09:05.071 --> 09:06.639
Banana Barbara:
Terrible aftershave!

09:06.672 --> 09:08.341
Taxi driver: Stinks of Banana!
One star!

09:08.374 --> 09:09.509
Larry!

09:09.542 --> 09:11.077
[ Tires screech ]
Oh, what now?!

09:11.111 --> 09:13.045
You're the only one
with a high-enough rating!

09:13.079 --> 09:15.148
You've got to give the website
zero stars!

09:15.181 --> 09:16.582
Sure. Right away.

09:16.616 --> 09:17.817
Wait a minute!

09:17.850 --> 09:20.153
I'll do it
on one condition.

09:20.186 --> 09:21.154
Anything!

09:21.187 --> 09:24.757
Someone has to admit
he's bald.

09:24.790 --> 09:26.992
[ Sighs ]
Of course.

09:27.026 --> 09:28.494
I understand.

09:28.528 --> 09:29.895
Darwin,
just tell him you're bald.

09:29.929 --> 09:32.998
What?! I'm not bald!
I have a healthy head of scales!

09:33.032 --> 09:33.966
Oh, come on!

09:33.999 --> 09:36.001
[ Sighing ]
Oh, you're right.

09:36.035 --> 09:38.638
Gumball, just tell --
You! You! It's you!

09:38.671 --> 09:40.473
Bald!
You are a bald!

09:40.506 --> 09:42.275
I'm not bald!

09:42.308 --> 09:45.077
Fine. Then I'll give the website
a five-star review,

09:45.111 --> 09:47.547
and it will become
unstoppable!

09:47.580 --> 09:48.548
Both: No!

09:48.581 --> 09:49.749
Dad: [ Gasps ]

09:49.782 --> 09:51.584
I'm not bald!

09:51.617 --> 09:53.486
I'm not bald!

09:53.519 --> 09:55.788
[ Gothic choir singing ]

09:58.057 --> 10:01.794
[ Screaming ]

10:01.827 --> 10:03.229
[ Both scream ]

10:12.238 --> 10:15.074
Yay! I can go back to not caring
what anybody thinks!

10:15.107 --> 10:17.076
Yay! I can go back
to treating

10:17.109 --> 10:19.111
other people's mail
like garbage!

10:19.145 --> 10:21.381
Yay!
I can get back to running!

10:21.414 --> 10:22.382
Hooray.

10:22.415 --> 10:23.916
[ Bicycle bell clangs ]

10:23.949 --> 10:25.618
What the --
The website's down.

10:25.651 --> 10:26.819
Both:
Yeah! You did it!

10:26.852 --> 10:27.953
You gave it
zero stars!

10:27.987 --> 10:29.989
Gah!
This is all your fault!

10:30.022 --> 10:32.124
The sunlight bounced off
the top of your head!

10:32.158 --> 10:34.727
